    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:1rem; font-weight:300; line-height:1.8; color:#4a4540; margin-bottom:1.25rem;">
      The proximity to Sunnybank's food precinct and community infrastructure adds a lifestyle dimension that complements Macgregor's residential qualities. Garden City in Upper Mount Gravatt provides major retail access, and Pacific Motorway connectivity gives residents straightforward access to the Brisbane CBD and Gold Coast. For families with school-age children, Macgregor's school catchments represent a genuine practical asset, and the suburb's established residential streets and local park network contribute to a neighbourhood character that buyers recognise and return for.
    </p>
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:1rem; font-weight:300; line-height:1.8; color:#4a4540; margin-bottom:1.25rem;">
