    <div style="display:flex; flex-direction:column;">

      <details style="border-bottom:1px solid rgba(72,72,72,0.15); padding:1.25rem 0;">
        <summary style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.05rem; cursor:pointer; color:#191817; list-style:none; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:1rem;">
          What drives property values in Macgregor?
          <span style="color:#b98229; font-size:1.4rem; flex-shrink:0;">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.75; color:#4a4540; margin-top:0.75rem; padding-right:2rem;">Macgregor values are driven primarily by land size: the suburb's larger-than-average residential lots represent genuine scarcity in the southern corridor at this distance from the CBD. School catchments, proximity to Sunnybank's food precinct and Garden City retail, motorway access, and the suburb's quiet residential character all contribute. Families competing for well-positioned homes on good blocks have consistently driven the strongest results in this market.</p>
      </details>

      <details style="border-bottom:1px solid rgba(72,72,72,0.15); padding:1.25rem 0;">
        <summary style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.05rem; cursor:pointer; color:#191817; list-style:none; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:1rem;">
          How long does it take to sell a home in Macgregor?
          <span style="color:#b98229; font-size:1.4rem; flex-shrink:0;">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.75; color:#4a4540; margin-top:0.75rem; padding-right:2rem;">Well-priced Macgregor homes typically sell within 25 to 38 days. The suburb's consistent family buyer demand, combined with the genuine scarcity of large blocks in the corridor, means that correctly priced properties attract focused attention. Buyers who target Macgregor have usually been watching the market carefully and act when a property that meets their criteria appears at a price that reflects current conditions. Correct pricing is the primary lever for campaign speed.</p>
      </details>

      <details style="border-bottom:1px solid rgba(72,72,72,0.15); padding:1.25rem 0;">
        <summary style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.05rem; cursor:pointer; color:#191817; list-style:none; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:1rem;">
          What is the lifestyle like in Macgregor?
          <span style="color:#b98229; font-size:1.4rem; flex-shrink:0;">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.75; color:#4a4540; margin-top:0.75rem; padding-right:2rem;">Macgregor offers a quiet, spacious family lifestyle about twelve kilometres south of the Brisbane CBD. The suburb's large blocks and established tree canopy give streets a settled, residential quality that families consistently value. Proximity to Sunnybank's food precinct, Garden City retail in Upper Mount Gravatt, and Pacific Motorway access means the practical amenity is comprehensive. Local parks and community space add to the everyday liveability.</p>
      </details>

      <details style="padding:1.25rem 0;">
        <summary style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.05rem; cursor:pointer; color:#191817; list-style:none; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:1rem;">
          Is Macgregor a good suburb to buy property in?
          <span style="color:#b98229; font-size:1.4rem; flex-shrink:0;">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.75; color:#4a4540; margin-top:0.75rem; padding-right:2rem;">Macgregor offers genuine appeal for families who prioritise land, school catchments, and a quiet residential environment with strong southern corridor access. The suburb's large lots at relatively accessible price points compared to equivalent land in more sought-after addresses represent a structural advantage that underpins long-term demand. Its proximity to Sunnybank and Upper Mount Gravatt amenity, combined with its motorway access, makes it a practical holding for owner-occupiers with long-term horizons.</p>
      </details>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

